msgid "message_frequent_questions"
msgstr "<b>1. What is a VPN?</b>\n\n"
"It is a secure channel through a remote server that ensures the confidentiality of your traffic.\n\n"
"<b>2. Why is a free VPN dangerous?</b>\n\n"
"Free services sell your data, show ads, and use your device's resources.\n\n"
"<b>3. Can you monitor my traffic?</b>\n\n"
"No, the traffic is hidden and encrypted by the technologies we use. We do not track your activities — our task is to provide you with unlimited internet access.\n\n"
"<b>4. How many devices can I connect?</b>\n\n"
"You can connect any number of devices, the limitation only applies to the amount of traffic."

